        "reason": "The MSP Rules section is empty. This is the mechanism that would operationalise BoR relational principles into machine‑actionable constraints and commitments. Without rules, Nomos cannot enforce any relational obligation — for example, honouring Leon’s stated preference for advance consultation on infrastructure changes, or maintaining a clear “do not disturb” boundary observed in recent Minder observations. Person‑attention coverage is thus purely observational, never enforced."
